     <body>
     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>To the deuout Reader.</head>
   <l>
      <hi>Iuditious reader if thou seeke to please</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>The fantasie, with Arguments of witt,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>Curious conceites; know such fond passages</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>I doe bequeath to lighter subiects fitt</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>To thy deuotion therfore (as a Frend)</hi>
   </l>
   <l>
      <hi>My matter, not my Meathhoode I commend.</hi>
   </l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Thine G. P.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
